'''Gadgets''' are toggleable perks available from the class selection screen. Gadgets are unlocked by upgrading the Gadget Workbench in the [[Basecamp]]. All gadgets are accessible to all classes. There are currently 17 gadgets available in [[Roboquest]].
The player starts with 1 gadget equip space, though can upgrade the Gadget Workbench for an additional 2 spaces. 2 gadgets currently require 2 equip spaces in order to use - the Rocketpants and the Jetpack.
